00:03:03.870 --> 00:03:07.920 align:middle line:84%
is actually disrupting
vital physiological systems

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:08.805 align:middle line:90%
in our body.

00:03:08.805 --> 00:03:12.527 align:middle line:84%
